 Faculty profile 

 
 

  Walt  Scacchi</strong>  Sr. Research Scientist, Institute for Software Research</strong>  DEGREE: Ph.D. 1981, UC Irvine  RESEARCH AREAS:  Computer-Supported Cooperative Work Software Engineering  RESEARCH INTERESTS:  Game culture and technology, game-based virtual worlds, virtual worlds as decentralized collaborative work environments, science learning games  CONTACT INFORMATION:            
                    
